Package: thunderclaw
Version: __VERSION__
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 18)
Suggests: thunderbird (>= 128)
Maintainer: pekinlcc <pekinlcc@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/pekinlcc/thunderclaw
Description: AI mail assistant for Thunderbird
 ThunderClaw is a Thunderbird extension that groups your local mail
 by contact, runs LLM analysis per contact via your locally logged-in
 Claude Code or Codex CLI, and surfaces a daily briefing of "things
 to act on today" — all on-device, no API keys, no cloud uploads.
 .
 This package bundles the Thunderbird extension and its native
 messaging host. After installation, restart Thunderbird and the
 AI 助手 space appears in the spaces toolbar.
